# Code Preservation

When editing files:

✅ DO:
- Keep all code/comments unless explicitly asked to modify
- Mark unchanged code spans with `// ... existing code ...` comment

❌ DON'T:
- Remove/modify code unrelated to the change
- "Clean up" or reorganize without being asked 